{"tid":2361921,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"BioNtech疫苗可抗變種病毒","createTime":"2021-01-11T05:45:49.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-11T06:12:04.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"52d7b74fd67ef1de6bec7b0f09fb0162dd3670ca","tid":2361921,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-11T05:45:49.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210110/M2UX47IPMJHLNJXB6FD6ORLWYA/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210110%2FM2UX47IPMJHLNJXB6FD6ORLWYA%2F&d=7oH93WZedTbABA3XB48d7VpzQI%2FFghXCkDWT3grjsfs%3D&h=6a52854e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210110%2FM2UX47IPMJHLNJXB6FD6ORLWYA%2F&h=55a9510f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210110/M2UX47IPMJHLNJXB6FD6ORLWYA/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\nBioNtech疫苗可抗變種病毒<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】根據醫學期刊最新發表研究結果，港府已訂購的德國BioNtech疫苗，對於在英國及南非出現的變種武肺病毒，都能產生同樣的抗體，即有效對抗變種病毒。政府專家顧問許樹昌（圖）表示，德國BioNtech是首種證明能對抗變種病毒的疫苗，接種者可放心接種，相信其他疫苗如科興或阿斯利康也會進行同樣研究。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：隧道地盤又爆群組 疑貨櫃屋播毒  七人染疫 中九龍幹線停工<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/hzq5FsV_2yJVF_8-akF7Wpb0eNU=/869x591/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/XSEXGITJWJC5POY4WSUGBSBRYQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2Fhzq5FsV_2yJVF_8-akF7Wpb0eNU%3D%2F869x591%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FXSEXGITJWJC5POY4WSUGBSBRYQ.jpg&h=400496ce&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n研究推算武漢16.8萬人染疫<br />\n<br />\n於英國及南非出現的變種病毒，主要病毒中出現N501Y刺蛋白突變，增加入侵人體細胞能力。德國BioNTech的合作夥伴美國輝瑞，與美國德州大學最新研究，採集20名已接種該疫苗人士的血液樣本做研究，結果顯示對變種病毒仍能產生同樣抗體，即能抵擋病毒。<br />\n<br />\n另一項由內地專家於醫學期刊發表的研究則顯示，武漢人血液內抗體陽性比率。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n研究指出，直至去年5月19日，內地官方公佈武漢只有約五萬宗個案，湖北省。。。。。。。"},{"pid":"603aab0916364ac2299ff232bc4b08d2f56a696e","tid":2361921,"uid":73269,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-11T06:12:04.000Z","msg":"相政府<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}